name: Bozik´na vecera
additionalNotes: Božik´na vecera is a very compex combinations, Ometepe tobaccos, Dominican Piloto, Mexican San Andres, Corojo 99 while all being wrapped up with a toothy Broadleaf Maduro wrapper. Box Press 6x52. Limited to only 200 burlap packages containing 5 meals. If you havent googled it already lol, Božik´na vecera translates to Christmas Dinner.
